name: Feed the Snake (LeibnizKeks)
description:
Control the snake to eat as many critters as you can.
Use A, D to steer the snake.
Use W, S to control the speed.

If your hunger bar fills up, you starve.
If your hunger bar goes empty, the snake will become longer.
Critters cannot move through your snake body, use this to trap faster critter.
Touching your own body won't kill you.
